<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-2598] Add check for minimum Go version to configure.ac</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2598</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Go build currently fails, if some older Go version is installed, e.g. because of missing &lt;tt&gt;io.ByteWriter&lt;/tt&gt;. Need to add appropriate check in configure.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
